{
  "stem": "11000.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "That means, you know, just be strong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It's not going to last, you know, that long, anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It's just a period we have to try to get over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I remember the whole country went on a nationwide strike to demonstrate that they do not approve of the way the Nazis treat their Jewish citizens.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But then of course, the Germans were capable of handling situations like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And they arrested many good people and sent them to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And many of them did not return.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly non-Jews, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember the Germans took over a Jewish bank in Amsterdam called Lippmann, Rosenthal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all Jews in Holland had to send their-- transfer their bank accounts, savings accounts, business accounts, to this particular bank.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All their holdings, all their stocks, or bonds, or whatever, birth certificates, everything had to be sent to Lippmann, Rosenthal, which then, of course, was taken over by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Things became known that eventually, Jews would be deported.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was presented in such a way that, OK, here we are, your masters, so to speak of.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we need labor in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they were fighting on the east front, and on the west front, and in Africa.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you will be forced to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] work for us until this war, of course, over, which we will win.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then will things probably go back to normal, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] whoever thought of a final solution as it was planned.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we used to get instructions from what they called the [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Joodsche  Raad, ?] the Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
